name: lesmis
description: Les Miserables is a social network dataset from the Social Networks Research Group at the University of California, Irvine. This graph depicts the coappearance relationships in the novel Les Miserables.

graph.name: lesmis
graph.semantic: The coappearance relationship of the characters in French novel Les Miserables.
